<!-- Template: 文艺风格-变体4 (Content #1554) - 诗歌意境 -->
<div class="w-[1440px] h-[810px] relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #FAF9F6; font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-[3px] h-full" style="background-color: #78350F;"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col px-14 py-10">
        <!-- 标题 -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-5">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-10 rounded-full flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #78350F;"></div>
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-[38px] font-bold" style="color: #292524;">诗歌意境</h1>
                <p class="text-[13px]" style="color: #A8A29E;">The Realm of Poetry</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 正文 -->
        <div class="mb-5 p-5 rounded-lg" style="background-color: #F5F5F4; border-left: 3px solid #78350F;">
            <p class="text-[16px] leading-loose" style="color: #57534E;">诗歌是语言的精华，是灵魂最纯粹的表达。它用最少的文字，承载最深沉的情感。在诗歌中，平凡的事物被赋予了不凡的意义。</p>
        </div>
        <!-- 诗歌展示 -->
        <div class="flex-1 flex gap-5">
            <!-- 三首诗 -->
            <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-4">
                <div class="flex-1 rounded-lg p-6 flex flex-col justify-center" style="background-color: #292524;">
                    <p class="text-[13px] mb-3" style="color: #A8A29E;">唐·李白</p>
                    <p class="text-[18px] leading-loose" style="color: #F5F5F4;">床前明月光，疑是地上霜。<br/>举头望明月，低头思故乡。</p>
                    <p class="text-[13px] mt-3 italic" style="color: #78716C;">— 《静夜思》</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 rounded-lg p-6 flex flex-col justify-center" style="background-color: #44403C;">
                    <p class="text-[13px] mb-3" style="color: #A8A29E;">宋·苏轼</p>
                    <p class="text-[18px] leading-loose" style="color: #F5F5F4;">但愿人长久，千里共婵娟。</p>
                    <p class="text-[13px] mt-3 italic" style="color: #78716C;">— 《水调歌头》</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- 右侧 -->
            <div class="w-[400px] flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col gap-4">
                <div class="flex-1 rounded-lg p-6 flex flex-col justify-center text-center" style="background-color: #FEF3C7;">
                    <div class="text-[28px] mb-2" style="color: #B45309;">"</div>
                    <p class="text-[16px] leading-loose italic" style="color: #57534E;">诗者，志之所之也。<br/>在心为志，发言为诗。</p>
                    <p class="text-[13px] mt-3" style="color: #A8A29E;">— 《毛诗序》</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-lg p-5" style="background-color: #FFFFFF; border: 1px solid #E7E5E4;">
                    <h3 class="text-[16px] font-bold mb-3" style="color: #292524;">诗歌的力量</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[14px]" style="color: #57534E;"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #78350F;"></span>凝练情感，直抵心灵</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[14px]" style="color: #57534E;"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #78350F;"></span>超越时空，永恒共鸣</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[14px]" style="color: #57534E;"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #78350F;"></span>启迪智慧，滋养灵魂</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background-color: #F5F5F4;">
                    <p class="text-[12px]" style="color: #A8A29E;">诗歌是文学的最高形式，每一个字都值得细细品味。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
